---
title: Ginger Green Onion Barramundi with Stir-Fried Veggies and Jasmine Rice
description: Put your table manners to the side just for tonight – and dig into this delectable stir-fry. Along with beautiful pan-seared barramundi, this colourful bowl is perfectly satisfying on a hectic weeknight.
